      <title>特朗普解雇了负责监督旧金山 Presidio 的董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/us/trump-presidio-landmark-board-fired.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责监督这一国家历史地标的所有六名董事会成员均被解雇，这是政府重塑联邦官僚机构的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/us/trump-presidio-landmark-board-fired.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 01:59:12 GMT</pubDate>
